{"tid":2040372,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【日記】麻煩阿姐事跡，每日都想辭職","createTime":"2020-05-28T13:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T23:51:52.000Z","uid":205602,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a816a649ea4cfa82b0836420935d73350367316d","tid":2040372,"uid":205602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"公司正常返8點半，依家flexi hour ，可以揀返晏啲，當然放工時間照褪遲。<br />\n今朝架巴士唔知做乜遲咗成10分鐘，跟住又無端端塞車，結果就遲咗10分鐘先返到。<br />\n咁遲到始終係唔啱嘅，就諗住靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐底做嘢，點知就即刻俾人照肺：<br />\n點解會遲到？之前已經講過返9點嘅同事唔可以遲到，如果下次再遲你就返翻八半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係咁，交通情況係點我又預計唔到，flexi hour原意係返工唔使同人逼，疏導吓人流，依家遲一次半次就兇人要返正常時間，都唔知flex咗啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都未講我每日至少ot個半鐘都計住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ff5d5b555450ec8b7e8fcfd773043d81713dfb","tid":2040372,"uid":205602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"阿姐名句：你返咗一個月㗎啦喎咁都唔識？"},{"pid":"fae5d6adaf5da158564e90bf576f3dbc16b7336d","tid":2040372,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"你話好多曱甴查巴士"},{"pid":"b4a03ba9053100d19374479c4c457c994fdcb31c","tid":2040372,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"抵啦遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6ba883da75a406d88d7623b66f83b8dc1d0a39","tid":2040372,"uid":257184,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"中學未比人鬧夠咩，唔係唔知答自己因為交通遲到會比人屌呀嘛？遲到都仲可以咁大口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己冇錯咁款，岩嫁啦，你咪辭職囉，下份工繼續比人屌"},{"pid"